in v19 `forRoot Called` will be console logged twice while in v18 it will be once in development build

```@NgModule({})
class TestModule {
  static forRoot(): ModuleWithProviders<TestModule> {
    console.log('forRoot Called');
    return {
      ngModule: TestModule,
    };
  }
}

@NgModule({
  declarations: [
    AppComponent
  ],
  imports: [
    BrowserModule,
    TestModule.forRoot()
  ],
  providers: [],
  bootstrap: [AppComponent]
})
export class AppModule { }
```

